        jLabel6.setText("<html>Although intermittent fasting is safe for well-nourished and healthy people, it does not suit everyone. Some studies note that it’s not as beneficial for women as it is for men (117Trusted Source, 118Trusted Source). In addition, some people should avoid fasting, including those sensitive to drops in blood sugar levels, pregnant women, breastfeeding moms, teenagers, children, and people who are malnourished, underweight, or nutrient deficient.</html>");
